overview: Anna is a very curvaceous and very dynamic young woman. As a tour guide, she organises personalized visits for young couples who want to go off the beaten tracks. With her looks and her charisma, she's sure to hit the right sport and all her clients are delighted by her stories and anecdotes. Very often, Anna becomes friends with her customers. Usually, they end up having a dring... and much more.
title: Anna, the Tour Guide
